{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/script-element/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Fei"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"7d1e82b8-9bd1-5430-b7ab-4223ac890696","excerpt":"使用标签的方式有两种：在页面中嵌入 JavaScript 代码和引入外部 JavaScript 文件。 在页面中嵌入 JavaScript 代码，其格式如下： 引入外部 JavaScript 文件，其格式如下： 二者不可混合，若出现下列情况，则只执行引入的外部 JavaScript…","html":"<p>使用<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;script&gt;</code>标签的方式有两种：在页面中嵌入 JavaScript 代码和引入外部 JavaScript 文件。</p>\n<p>在页面中嵌入 JavaScript 代码，其格式如下：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'biped.me'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>引入外部 JavaScript 文件，其格式如下：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'example.js'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>二者不可混合，若出现下列情况，则只执行引入的外部 JavaScript 文件。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'example.js'</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token comment\">// 下列代码会被忽略 console.log('biped.me');&lt;/script></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>通常使用<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;script&gt;</code>标签时，<code class=\"language-text\">type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;</code>这个属性较为常见。它的意思是指定 MIME 类型为<code class=\"language-text\">text/javascript</code>，但实际上服务器传输 JavaScript 文件时使用的 MIME 类型是<code class=\"language-text\">application/x-javascript</code>。由于<code class=\"language-text\">type</code>属性可选，故而使用<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;script&gt;</code>标签时可直接省略<code class=\"language-text\">type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;</code>，这在真实开发过程中较为常用。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 可以省略 type=\"text/javascript\"</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script type<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'text/javascript'</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'biped.me'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;script&gt;</code>标签的<code class=\"language-text\">src</code>属性既可以引入站内 JavaScript 文件，也可以引入站外 JavaScript 文件。这一点通常用来使用公共 CDN 加快网站访问速度，但选择站外 JavaScript 文件来源需慎重，因为文件内容不可控。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 如使用CDN引入jQuery</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'http://cdn.staticfile.org/jquery/1.11.1/jquery.min.js'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>在 XHMTL 文档中可省略结束标签<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;/script&gt;</code>，但不能在 HTML 文档中这么做。因为它不符合规范，且无法被 IE 正确解析。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 在XHTML文档中符合规范，但在HTML文档中无法通过验证</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'example.js'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;script&gt;</code>标签通常被放在文档中的<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;head&gt;</code>标签内，但这样做意味着页面内容的展示需要等到所有 JavaScript 全部下载、解析和执行完成以后，在此期间用户看到的是一片空白，体验糟糕。为此，通常将<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;script&gt;</code>标签放在<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;body&gt;</code>标签内、<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;/body&gt;</code>标签前，以增强用户体验。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>biped.me<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- content here --></span>\n\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>example1.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>example2.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>example3.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"script标签","date":"2015-01-21","description":"script 标签天天见，但你真的懂它吗？"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/script-element/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/echarts-gauge-negative-value/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"ECharts仪表盘正负值"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/setting-up-jshint/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"配置JSHint"}}}}}